      serialVersionUID:
      1L

      • Serialized Fields

        • createTime

        • createUser

        • id
          Long id
          The unique identifier for the pet detail.
        • isDeleted
          Integer isDeleted
          Indicates whether this pet detail has been deleted. This field is used for logical deletion of records and is not included in select queries.
        • name
          String name
          The name of the pet detail (e.g., "Breed", "Color").
        • petId
          Long petId
          The unique identifier for the associated pet. This links the detail to a specific pet in the system.
        • updateTime
          LocalDateTime updateTime
          The date and time when this pet detail was last updated. This field is automatically filled during both insertions and updates.
        • updateUser
          Long updateUser
          The ID of the user who last updated this pet detail. This field is automatically filled during both insertions and updates.
        • value
          String value
          The value of the pet detail (e.g., "Golden Retriever", "Brown").
